  <div class="section-content">
    <h3 class="section-title"><span class="title-accent emoji-replace">about</span> <span class="mobile-hide">me</span></h3>
    <p class="scroll-reveal-effect mobile-hide">Greetings! I'm a web developer passionate about merging creativity with technology to craft stunning, interactive online experiences. My journey from the hospitality industry to web development has equipped me with a unique blend of skills, allowing me to manage multiple projects efficiently while fostering outstanding teamwork and client relationships. This background has been instrumental in my approach to web development, pushing me to innovate and consistently exceed expectations. 
      
